The dagger contains, among others, the soul of Major Corwin's former lover, Beno Famari.~
@4016 = ~Though this appears to be the Soultaker dagger, it is different somehow. It doesn't feel as heavy as it did, and you don't feel that palpable sense of dread that you did when you found it in Amn. The gem in the hilt is dark and lifeless. Odd.~
