@45913 = ~This heavy slab displays the holy symbol of Tempus.~
@45914 = ~This magical barrier hums with arcane power. Beyond, the camp buzzes with activity as the crusaders prepare for battle.~
@45915 = ~A translucent field of force glimmers before the gate, its magic repelling any attempt to enter the courtyard.~
@45916 = ~Though the crusade's symbol is a sun upon the horizon, this banner offers little warmth or light to the oppressive gloom permeating Dragonspear Castle.~
@45917 = ~Properly positioned, this recently repaired catapult could inflict serious damage upon Caelar's enemies.~
