@45961 = ~Ring of Free Action~
@45962 = ~A ring is a small band of precious metal that is used as jewelry. Some rare rings have had enchantments placed upon them that confer various magical abilities. These rings are highly sought after, especially by those of the adventuring profession.

STATISTICS:

Weight: 0~
@45963 = ~Enemies have a hard time slowing this ring's wearer down. The runes etched in the silver band ward off spells designed to impede movement, granting its owner a freedom of mobility others affected by such magic are denied.

STATISTICS:

