@45964 = ~Battle Axe~
@45965 = ~Chill Axe +2~
@45966 = ~The most common version of the battle axe is a stout pole about four feet in length with a single-edged, trumpet-shaped blade mounted on one end. Battle axes are also called broad axes.

STATISTICS:

Damage: 1d8 (slashing)
Speed Factor: 7
Proficiency Type: Axe
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 10 Strength

Weight: 7~
@45967 = ~This finely crafted axe bears the sigil of the Ice Dragon Berserker Lodge. Glowing white runes edge its cold silver blade, and a cloud of chill air trails behind the axe whenever it is swung. The most powerful rangers of the Ice Dragon Berserker Lodge carry these axes with them on their dejemmas, as protection from southern threats.

