@50674 = ~Amulet of Abnormally Awesome Ankheg Summoning~
@50675 = ~Amulets are usually magical devices that are commonly worn around the neck, suspended from a chain. The type of chain that comes with an amulet generally increases the item's aesthetic value, not its magical properties. Only one amulet can be dangled from the neck at a time.

STATISTICS:

Weight: 1~
